<!-- An inline element that wraps, preceded by another inline node (element or expression tag) across a space, breaks to a fresh line with no stray leading space (idempotent). -->
<p>word1 word2 word3 word4 word5 word6 word7 word8 word9 word10 word11 <span>x</span> <a href="/a/b">content</a> tail</p>
<p>word1 word2 word3 word4 word5 word6 word7 word8 word9 word10 word11 word12 {x} <a href="/a/b">content</a> tail</p>
